  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773160/extras/e82fb71fc0c2aea0dc352674ccda32cb.webp?t=1735876270\" width=600 height=31 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drawing is your power</h2>Draw gestures to attack and dodge, unleashing spells with your right hand and dodging enemy attacks with your left. Experience a uniquely enchanting adventure designed for maximum fun. Welcome to Magic Caster, where magic is in your hands!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featured Content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience thrilling monster behaviour with growing challenges at every level.<br></li><li>Face tough bosses in a magical world with campaign and boss modes.<br></li><li>Collect spells, wands, and pets to enhance your magical abilities.<br></li><li>Compete on leaderboards in Endless mode, and Bosses mode.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773160/extras/6e035c9e905a6680d69adb032e1f3c80.poster.avif?t=1735876270\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773160/extras/6e035c9e905a6680d69adb032e1f3c80.webm?t=1735876270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773160/extras/6e035c9e905a6680d69adb032e1f3c80.mp4?t=1735876270\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773160/extras/8cc3d568820b3c6b0351bf8707862709.poster.avif?t=1735876270\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2773160/extras/8cc3d568820b3c6b0351bf8707862709.webm?t=1735876270\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://sh